The alleged mastermind behind the Tshegofatso Pule murder, Nthuthuko Shoba. eNCA/Silindelo Masikane JOHANNESBURG - Tshegofatso Pule's murder case against Ntuthuko Shoba has been reopened. Shoba submitted CCTV footage as new evidence. The alleged mastermind believes the evidence will sway the judge. eNCA’s Slindelo Masikane reports. Courtesy #DStv403 #eNCA